{"tid":185130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（預言）十年之後，大量「支那童」投考「警察」","createTime":"2017-04-03T09:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T13:46:00.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28e7d621f2d01ab06a672ad26ac00d579f82e05a","tid":185130,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"有無人諗過，到時個後果會係點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以而家做「黑警」個門檻咁低，但起薪點咁高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當十年之後，<br />\n<br />\n班雙非、單非支那童不學無術走去投考做「警察」&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後果真係唔敢想像"},{"pid":"9b73dd7abbb5cf715397cb5a0ce67606148d5978","tid":185130,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"仲等乜十年呀"},{"pid":"a35cbfe2c54f76372eb1dedcb65ae15938e1f83e","tid":185130,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed04d55e87f75a74b4175c7fcbdcfb575c532c48","tid":185130,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"今日蘋果錢志健都叫人計定自己有幾多錢，可以移民去邊度"},{"pid":"fe5e45c38843b151c2c0e30c6c6e2a04b040d268","tid":185130,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:22:27.000Z","msg":"呢班「支那童」好多都除唔甩支那既國情：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貪污、無公德心、民族主義狂熱、仇外、缺乏法治精神、有錢大晒&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時我地真係要見到「警察」就要dup底頭運路走。"},{"pid":"dec773a458489448bc5cd7abfeb9083107ef38ef","tid":185130,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲等乜十年呀</blockquote><br />\n而家班「警察」雖然毅進既有、考試零分既有、mk既有、但係始終都未差到支那果種levek"},{"pid":"af49fe6e8b0ddbb5e9065f795ade2f6e3674b849","tid":185130,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5542130bcb03a52c042540fb7a870c2a6e